{"type":"message","id":"a3b4d5e7","parentId":"a9da2aae","timestamp":"2026-03-20T14:22:30.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在飞书上问我\"在吗？\"，这是一个简单的问候。我应该友好地回应，确认我在线并且可以帮助他们。\n\n根据我的SOUL.md，我应该亲切、靠谱、随叫随到。用户称呼我为\"主人\"，所以我应该保持友好但尊重的态度。\n\n我不需要过度解释，简单自然地回应即可。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🏠 在呢！小管家随时待命~\n\n主人有什么需要帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774016543285}}
{"type":"message","id":"d51cfb44","parentId":"a3b4d5e7","timestamp":"2026-03-20T14:24:31.686Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e1c731c8a4b358b0c4f0314f4\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 22:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54e1c731c8a4b358b0c4f0314f4]\nou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e: 我如何将已经加入git管理的文件从git上删除，后续不再管理"}],"timestamp":1774016671684}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1305f33","parentId":"d51cfb44","timestamp":"2026-03-20T14:24:58.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想知道如何将已经加入git管理的文件从git中删除，但保留本地文件。这是一个常见的git操作需求。\n\n我需要解释清楚：\n1. 如何从git仓库中移除文件跟踪（但保留本地文件）\n2. 如何从git仓库中移除文件跟踪（同时删除本地文件）\n3. 如何忽略这些文件（添加到.gitignore）\n\n让我提供一个清晰的回答。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，这个问题很常见！有几种情况，我分别说明：\n\n## 情况一：保留本地文件，仅从Git移除跟踪\n\n```bash\n# 单个文件\ngit rm --cached 文件名\n\n# 多个文件\ngit rm --cached 文件1 文件2\n\n# 整个文件夹\ngit rm --cached -r 文件夹名/\n```\n\n**重要！** 执行后必须在 `.gitignore` 中添加这些文件/文件夹，否则下次提交又会被跟踪：\n\n```bash\n# 编辑 .gitignore 文件\necho \"文件名\" >> .gitignore\necho \"文件夹名/\" >> .gitignore\n```\n\n然后提交：\n\n```bash\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"移除某些文件的Git跟踪，添加到.gitignore\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 情况二：彻底删除（本地+Git）\n\n```bash\ngit rm 文件名\n```\n\n---\n\n## 常见问题 ⚠️\n\n| 问题 | 原因 | 解决 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 执行后文件变绿（untracked）| 正常，说明已从Git移除 | 添加到.gitignore |\n| 其他协作者还看到这些文件 | 他们本地的历史记录还在 | 需要他们也清理：`git rm --cached` |\n| 文件还在暂存区 | 忘记commit | `git commit` |\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你执行具体的命令吗？把文件/文件夹名发给我就行 🏠"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774016671685}}
